name: Ext_R5_HealthcareService_photo
title: Cross-version Extension for R5.HealthcareService.photo for use in FHIR R4
description: This cross-version extension represents HealthcareService.photo from http://hl7.org/fhir/StructureDefinition/HealthcareService|5.0.0 for use in FHIR R4.

element.short: Facilitates quick identification of the service
element.definition: If there is a photo/symbol associated with this HealthcareService, it may be included here to facilitate quick identification of the service in a list.
element.comment: `HealthcareService.photo` maps to R4 `HealthcareService.photo`. So is mapped as Equivalent.
